        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <p>The Placement Cell offers a range of services to support students in their career development and to assist recruiters in finding the right candidates. Below is a list of the services we provide:</p>
        
        <h3>Resume Building Workshops</h3>
        <p>We conduct workshops to help students create effective and professional resumes that stand out to potential employers. Our experts provide tips on formatting, content, and customization for different job roles.</p>
        
        <h3>Mock Interviews</h3>
        <p>We organize mock interview sessions to help students practice and improve their interview skills. These sessions are conducted by experienced professionals and provide valuable feedback to help students prepare for real job interviews.</p>
        
        <h3>On-campus Recruitment Drives</h3>
        <p>We host on-campus recruitment drives where top companies visit our campus to interview and hire students. This provides students with direct access to leading employers and increases their chances of securing a job.</p>
        
        <h3>Career Counseling</h3>
        <p>Our career counseling services offer personalized guidance to students regarding their career paths, job search strategies, and professional development. Our counselors help students identify their strengths and interests to make informed career choices.</p>
        
        <h3>Workshops and Seminars</h3>
        <p>We regularly organize workshops and seminars on various topics such as soft skills, technical skills, industry trends, and job market insights. These events are designed to enhance students' knowledge and prepare them for the professional world.</p>
        
        <h3>Internship Opportunities</h3>
        <p>We assist students in finding internship opportunities that provide valuable work experience and enhance their employability. Our network of industry partners helps us connect students with internships in their fields of interest.</p>
        
        <h3>Job Fairs</h3>
        <p>We organize job fairs that bring together employers and job seekers in one place. These events provide students with the opportunity to meet with multiple employers, learn about different companies, and apply for various job openings.</p>
        
        <h3>Alumni Networking</h3>
        <p>We facilitate networking opportunities with alumni who are established professionals in their respective fields. These connections can provide mentorship, career advice, and job referrals to current students.</p>
